  "build": {
    "buildCommand": "gh pr comment 23 --body \"$(cat <<'EOF'\n## 📋 dev 分支進度更新（2026-05-30）\n\n### ✅ 十四、Controller + Route 層完成（Issue #14 #15 #16）\n\n**`e0802ac` — feat(controllers): implement auth, user, room, and message controllers (#14 #15 #16)**\n\n#### 新增檔案\n\n| 檔案 | 說明 |\n|------|------|\n| `src/controllers/authController.ts` | `register` / `login` / `logout` |\n| `src/controllers/userController.ts` | `getMe` / `updateMe` / `search` |\n| `src/controllers/roomController.ts` | `list` / `createGroup` / `getById` / `update` / `joinByCode` / `leave` |\n| `src/controllers/messageController.ts` | `listForRoom`（cursor pagination） |\n| `src/routes/authRoutes.ts` | `POST /auth/register`, `POST /auth/login`, `POST /auth/logout` |\n| `src/routes/userRoutes.ts` | `GET /users/me`, `PATCH /users/me`, `GET /users/search` |\n| `src/routes/roomRoutes.ts` | `GET /rooms`, `POST /rooms/group`, `GET/PATCH /rooms/:id`, `POST /rooms/join/:code`, `DELETE /rooms/:id/leave` |\n| `src/routes/messageRoutes.ts` | `GET /rooms/:roomId/messages` |\n\n#### 修改檔案\n\n- **`index.ts`**：完全移除 inline SQL handler；改用工廠函式 DI，統一掛載 4 組 Router\n- **`roomService.ts`**：接受 `IRoomMemberRepository`；`create` 自動加入 creator 為 owner；`getById`/`update` 加入 membership/role 檢查；新增 `joinByCode`、`leave`\n- **`userService.ts`**：新增 `getMe`、`updateMe`、`search`\n- **`IUserRepository` + `UserRepository`**：新增 `search(query)` — ILIKE 姓名或精確比對 userId\n- **`IRoomRepository` + `RoomRepository`**：新增 `findByInviteCode(code)`\n- **`userSchemas.ts`**：新增 `updateMeSchema`、`searchQuerySchema`\n\n#### API 端點完整清單\n\n| Method | Path | Auth | Status |\n|--------|------|------|--------|\n| POST | `/auth/register` | — | 201 |\n| POST | `/auth/login` | — | 200 |\n| POST | `/auth/logout` | JWT | 204 |\n| GET | `/users/me` | JWT | 200 |\n| PATCH | `/users/me` | JWT | 200 |\n| GET | `/users/search?query=` | JWT | 200 |\n| GET | `/rooms` | JWT | 200 |\n| POST | `/rooms/group` | JWT | 201 |\n| GET | `/rooms/:id` | JWT | 200 |\n| PATCH | `/rooms/:id` | JWT (owner/admin) | 200 |\n| POST | `/rooms/join/:code` | JWT | 200 |\n| DELETE | `/rooms/:id/leave` | JWT | 204 |\n| GET | `/rooms/:roomId/messages` | JWT | 200 |\n\n`tsc --noEmit` 通過，無型別錯誤。\n同步更新 `docs/frontend_integration_guide.md`。\nEOF\n)\"",
